DESCRIPTION:<p>Review best practices for handling grievances and how to avo
 id common pitfalls\, mistakes and traps in our latest online workshop for G
 uild stewards. Experienced Teamster business agent and labor educator Richa
 rd DeVries will use a true-to-life scenario to explore the highs and lows o
 f grievance handling as a shop steward or business agent.</p><p>This is a 9
 0 minute workshop.</p><p><strong><b><a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/
 d/e/1FAIpQLScQWeJDnrIHxXhbQAbR2o-1gFIk6L2KApKr-r-kIsvwWsJvqQ/viewform?usp=s
 f_link"><b>REGISTER HERE</b></a></b></strong></p>
