DESCRIPTION:<html-blob>Last summer\, The New Yorker Union won a historic fi
 rst contract at the magazine after they turned up the heat and put a credib
 le strike threat on the table. Come hear from those workers about how they 
 did it\, what they learned\, and how you can do the same in your workplace.
 <br><br><a href="https://forms.gle/RgeTwHymER7mLJu6A" id="ow3133" __is_owne
 r="true">REGISTER HERE</a></html-blob>
