 d is convening a membership meeting at 8 p.m. ET on Thursday\, April 10th. 
 We'll discuss the threats to our union\, members and our industry. We'll he
 ar from Guild members in the field on how these threats are playing out and
  together we'll develop strategies and actions for a national campaign to D
 efend Our Free Press.<br><br>(NewsGuild-CWA members only)<br><br>Register h
 ere: <a href="https://us06web.zoom.us/meeting/register/dbmD_XJmQKGcXBs9-Y3j
