DESCRIPTION:Join us on the second Saturday of each month for the national M
 ember Organizer Program monthly meeting! Meet other member organizers from 
 around the country\, share challenges and wins\, and practice organizing sk
 ills.\n\nEach month\, a different member organizer pod will be responsible 
 for developing the agenda\, facilitating the meeting\, and sending out Zoom
  registration links in advance. Please reach out to Hil O'Connell at hoconn
 ell@cwa-union.org if you have any questions!
