DESCRIPTION:<br>IGN Creators Guild is boarding the battle bus for two of ou
 r favorite things: unions\, and video games! On Monday\, February 26 at 5pm
  PT/8pm ET on Twitch\, we'll be playing some Fortnite while chatting about 
 unionization and what's next for the IGN Creators Guild now that we've been
  voluntarily recognized by Ziff Davis. And we'll bring it all home by answe
 ring your questions about unionization live! Join us at <a href="http://twi
 tch.tv/newsguildcwa/">twitch.tv/newsguildcwa/</a> to celebrate our voluntar
 y recognition and learn a little more about what unions can do for all of u
 s!
