 ss how to handle supervisors who are trying to put you off or trip you up.&
 nbsp\;</p><p>Please fill out the information below and then select one of t
 he upcoming training dates to attend. The number of attendees is limited to
  ensure active participation in the workshop. New dates will be added as th
 e class fills up. If you sign up\, but then cannot attend\, then please ema
 il <a href="mailto:chris@nyguild.org">chris@nyguild.org</a>.&nbsp\;</p><p><
