CREATED:20250207T194242Z
DESCRIPTION:<p><strong>A new book featuring NewsGuild members is out now!</
 strong> <em>We Are the Union</em> by Eric Blanc focuses on the worker-to-wo
 rker model of organizing that revitalized the Guild\, Workers United and ot
 her unions. It provides a roadmap for workers building a movement by connec
 ting directly with each other. This is how the Guild’s Member Organizing Pr
 ogram works! Workers win their union\, then help other workers win their un
 ion.</p><p>Join us at 6 p.m. ET on Tuesday\, February 25th for a virtual ch
 at with author Eric Blanc about the impact of worker-to-worker organizing.<
 /p><br><span>NewsGuild members can use promo code UNION50 to buy a discount
 ed copy of the</span><span> </span><a href="https://www.ucpress.edu/books/w
 e-are-the-union/paper" target="_blank">book from the University of Californ
 ia Press</a><span>.<br></span><br>RSVP: <a href="https://actionnetwork.org/
 events/we-are-the-union-book-talk-with-eric-blanc">https://actionnetwork.or
 g/events/we-are-the-union-book-talk-with-eric-blanc</a>
LAST-MODIFIED:20250211T211508Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:'We Are The Union' Book Talk with Eric Blanc
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
