CREATED:20251105T151717Z
DESCRIPTION:<p dir="ltr"><b>Member organizers</b> are members from the rank
  and file who connect with workers from around the country to share experie
 nces\, develop skills\, and organize to build power within the labor moveme
 nt.</p>The <b>purpose</b> of the member organizer program is to strengthen 
 our union by developing our members to do the work of our union.<br><br>Com
 e join our Biannual meeting to meet members from around the country\, conne
 ct\, and brainstorm through organizing topics together.<br><br>Register her
 e for the zoom link: <a href="https://us06web.zoom.us/meeting/register/xKpB
 sIx4RUaDwhLyVe0sxQ">https://us06web.zoom.us/meeting/register/xKpBsIx4RUaDwh
 LyVe0sxQ</a>
