 ngs just plain boring? Well\, you are not alone! In this workshop we will d
 iscuss how to run effective meetings. Learn how to create a strong agenda\,
  stay on task\, get real work done\, and make the experience enjoyable in t
 he process!<br><br>Offered by The NewsGuild of New York.&nbsp\;<br>7-8 p.m.
  ET\, Nov. 30\, 2021<br>This will be a repeat of the training offered Nov. 
