DESCRIPTION:On <b>Saturday\, September 30\, 2023</b>\, we will be holding a
  NewsGuild-CWA union-wide <b>Strike School</b>.<br><br>This day-long remote
  training will serve as an opportunity to hear from workers at TNG and beyo
 nd who have been on strike\, learn practical skills necessary to prepare yo
 ur local and workshop your own shop’s escalation and organizing plan. We en
 courage locals with high interest to gather together in person and join us 
 remotely.<br><br>Sign up here: <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1
 FAIpQLSeabtLMFHiHgVK90Vdve76jSqEd63kKhfOK4-xiFFo2eGMTWw/viewform">https://d
 ocs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeabtLMFHiHgVK90Vdve76jSqEd63kKhfOK4-xiFFo2
 eGMTWw/viewform</a><br><br>And\, to receive the zoom link: <a href="https:/
 /us02web.zoom.us/meeting/register/tZUpde2uqT0iH9wmRDe-MlrpNnzCGuAIh1aB">htt
 ps://us02web.zoom.us/<wbr />meeting/register/<wbr />tZUpde2uqT0iH9wmRDe-<wb
 r />MlrpNnzCGuAIh1aB</a>
