DESCRIPTION:<p><a href="https://us02web.zoom.us/meeting/register/tZYvdu6orj
 kqH91Al24UN6af-WI7YEjVKj_D">REGISTERHERE.</a></p><p>This is chance for new 
 units — those who won union elections or voluntary recognition in the last 
 year — to meet\, connect\, learn and share.</p><p>LET’S JAM: We’ll share wh
 y we started our unions and what we’remost proud of<br>SHARING\, SETTING GO
 ALS: What do we want to accomplish in thenext 30 days? What’s the most impo
 rtant bargaining goal? <br>ORGANIZING YOUR COWORKERS: Now that you’re a uni
 on\, organizingisn’t over! It’s the core of what we do. We’ll talk about ho
 w organizing is socentral to our unions’ work. BARGAINING: We’ll hear from 
 one of our members who will sharethe ins-and-outs of bargaining and what yo
 u can expect<br>MEETINGS: A quick 101 on how to run effective meetings. <br
 >TRAIN TO WIN: The NewsGuild is loaded with great trainingopportunities. We
 ’ll share the latest list<br>BUILDING SOLIDARITY: We’ll have a jamboard rea
 dy for everyone toshare their contacts.&nbsp\;</p>
