DESCRIPTION:<p><a href="https://actionnetwork.org/events/how-to-protect-you
 rself-from-threats-before-and-after-they-happen" target="_blank">Click here
  to register!</a></p><p><span>The climate for journalists and media workers
  has become increasingly unsafe – especially online. With this in mind\, we
  reached out to Investigative Reporters and Editors Inc. (IRE) to plan a lu
 nch-hour webinar where you can learn </span><strong>how to protect yourself
  from online threats before and after they happen.</strong></p><p>At the se
 ssion - which will be held from <strong>1 to 2PM ET March 27 via Zoom </str
 ong>– you can learn how to put up safeguards to protect yourself\, how to r
 espond when your work and your safety are threatened\, and more.</p><p>The 
 event is <strong>free</strong> for NewsGuild members.<br></p>
