UID:2uif5sb6lqfq8qvpdurvj1rnoq@google.com
CREATED:20211220T232313Z
DESCRIPTION:<p><b>Thursday\, January 20 at 5 p.m. - 6:30 pm ET<u></u><u></u
 ></b></p><p><strong><a href="https://yorku.zoom.us/webinar/register/WN_1US4
 b_ksRf2rQ7fv1Lce9Q">Register to receive the Zoom link</a><br><a href="https
 ://glrc.info.yorku.ca/event/collective-action-works/" id="ow1016" __is_owne
 r="true">Read more.</a></strong><u></u><u></u></p><p>Labour journalist and 
 author&nbsp\;<strong>Sarah Jaffe</strong>&nbsp\;hosts a virtual forum on or
 ganizing in the media and cultural sectors.&nbsp\;<a href="https://cultural
 workersorganize.org/digital-media-organizing-timeline/">As the digital medi
 a union movement has not let up for more than five years now</a>\, and as t
 he pandemic begins to recede\, it’s time to take stock of what we’ve won\, 
 to reflect on new strategies\, and to frankly assess the challenges that li
 e ahead.<u></u><u></u></p><p>Watch:&nbsp\;<a href="https://can01.safelinks.
 protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDyT
 ETo6NUHs&amp\;data=04%7C01%7Cnicole.cohen%40utoronto.ca%7Cfa8a491fddf84c94a
 cd008d9b4fb8c0f%7C78aac2262f034b4d9037b46d56c55210%7C0%7C0%7C63773981474389
 5336%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQIjoiV2luMzIiLCJBTiI6Ik
 1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%3D%7C3000&amp\;sdata=ZpCY15XNkm4kRjdEQjkeVOQu6wLTBHw%2F3r
 7bVQuR78Q%3D&amp\;reserved=0">Organizing Digital Media</a><u></u><u></u></p
 ><p>Union members in new media and culture unions discuss what they’ve won 
 through collective bargaining\, what’s sustaining the push to organize amid
  the pandemic\, and how equity goals are reflected in their campaigns.<u></
 u><u></u></p><p>Featuring:<br><strong>Kaitlyn Chandler</strong>\, former Br
 ooklyn Academy of Music<b><br></b><strong>Marina Fang</strong>\, The HuffPo
 st Union<br><strong>Arshy Mann</strong>\, Canadaland Union<b><br></b><stron
 g>Naib Mian</strong>\, The New Yorker Union<br>Speaker TBD\, Oxford Univers
 ity Press Union<u></u><u></u></p><p>This event marks the launch of a short 
 video\,&nbsp\;<a href="https://can01.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=
 https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDyTETo6NUHs&amp\;data=04%7C01%7
 Cnicole.cohen%40utoronto.ca%7Cfa8a491fddf84c94acd008d9b4fb8c0f%7C78aac2262f
 034b4d9037b46d56c55210%7C0%7C0%7C637739814743895336%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d
 8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQIjoiV2luMzIiLCJBTiI6Ik1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%3D%7C3000&
 amp\;sdata=ZpCY15XNkm4kRjdEQjkeVOQu6wLTBHw%2F3r7bVQuR78Q%3D&amp\;reserved=0
 ">Organizing Digital Media</a>\, and the book&nbsp\;<a href="https://can01.
 safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fculturalworkersorganize
 .org%2Fnewmediaunions%2F&amp\;data=04%7C01%7Cnicole.cohen%40utoronto.ca%7Cf
 a8a491fddf84c94acd008d9b4fb8c0f%7C78aac2262f034b4d9037b46d56c55210%7C0%7C0%
 7C637739814743905330%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQIjoiV2
 luMzIiLCJBTiI6Ik1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%3D%7C3000&amp\;sdata=izSoeMbKaRDhCJgwKCBB
 4bnWHzHv0kAPz%2BO3GZk7tss%3D&amp\;reserved=0">New Media Unions: Organizing 
 Digital Journalists</a>&nbsp\;by&nbsp\;<strong>Nicole S. Cohen</strong>&nbs
 p\;(University of Toronto) and&nbsp\;<strong>Greig de Peuter</strong>&nbsp\
 ;(Wilfrid Laurier University).<u></u><u></u></p><p>Co-organized by&nbsp\;<a
  href="https://can01.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fdi
 gitalmediaunion.ca%2F&amp\;data=04%7C01%7Cnicole.cohen%40utoronto.ca%7Cfa8a
 491fddf84c94acd008d9b4fb8c0f%7C78aac2262f034b4d9037b46d56c55210%7C0%7C0%7C6
 37739814743905330%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQIjoiV2luM
 zIiLCJBTiI6Ik1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%3D%7C3000&amp\;sdata=kFhXtZgXUXz8eC51Z6olIPj
 ZudOt%2B5Tknn9H3mrhZxY%3D&amp\;reserved=0">CWA Canada</a>&nbsp\;and&nbsp\;<
 a href="https://can01.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fc
 ulturalworkersorganize.org%2F&amp\;data=04%7C01%7Cnicole.cohen%40utoronto.c
 a%7Cfa8a491fddf84c94acd008d9b4fb8c0f%7C78aac2262f034b4d9037b46d56c55210%7C0
 %7C0%7C637739814743915325%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQI
 joiV2luMzIiLCJBTiI6Ik1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%3D%7C3000&amp\;sdata=yf0UWK1MKfbG5o4
 pWf29TYPjzS%2B4JHl2vv4xNNDOyqE%3D&amp\;reserved=0">Cultural Workers Organiz
 e</a>&nbsp\;and hosted by the Global Labour Research Centre at York Univers
 ity.<u></u><u></u></p><p><u></u>&nbsp\;</p>
