UID:215kjaabgunf341p2na2obftkv@google.com
CREATED:20220825T180155Z
DESCRIPTION:<html-blob><u></u><p><b>Staff Side-by-Side Program</b> – The Ne
 wsGuildSide-by-Side Program is an exciting program to provide national and 
 local TNG staff with the opportunity to see each other in action and reflec
 t on our work! This peer observer model\, advocated by CWA\, has been an ef
 fective model for collaborative staff development.</p><p>Participants commi
 t to 1 hour per week for 4 weeks in beginningSept. 6 and ending Oct. 3.<b>&
 nbsp\;</b></p><p><b>Week of Sept. 6&nbsp\;</b>Buddies are introduced via em
 ail. Identify the top three opportunities you have this month that you’d li
 ke your buddy to observe.&nbsp\;</p><p><b>Sept. 12 at 12pm ET:</b> Kickoff 
 meeting.</p><p><b>Week of Sept. 19:</b> Shadow your buddy\, or vice versa.<
 /p><p><b>Week of Sept. 26:</b> Switch! Buddy shadows you\, or vice versa. D
 ebrief together and discuss what you both observed and what may be valuable
  to share back with the whole group during our debrief call at the end of t
 he month.</p><p><b>Oct. 3 at 12pm ET:</b> Debrief meeting.&nbsp\;</p><p><a 
 href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScbcg42M66mAfrY6kXW_-xqFHQxp
 eV2cwvTmqPM5eetOebLbA/viewform" id="ow1329" __is_owner="true">Register here
 </a>.<br></p><u></u></html-blob>
LAST-MODIFIED:20220825T181018Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Side-by-Side Kickoff
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
