UID:193a1m8ct9e82e98sine602c5k@google.com
CREATED:20250207T155908Z
DESCRIPTION:<p dir="ltr">Do you know a NewsGuild member who's been through 
 bargaining\, wants to learn more and then help bargain contracts alongside 
 other Guild members? If so\, apply for the Guild's Member Bargaining Bootca
 mp.</p><p dir="ltr"><span>The program has five two-hour trainings over seve
 ral weeks. Members must commit to attending all the sessions and a few othe
 r meetings barring an emergency. </span></p><p dir="ltr"><span>Register her
