DESCRIPTION:<html-blob><p><b>Staff Side-by-Side Program</b>&nbsp\;– The New
 sGuildSide-by-Side Program is an exciting program to provide national and l
 ocal TNG staff with the opportunity to see each other in action and reflect
  on our work! This peer observer model\, advocated by CWA\, has been an eff
 ective model for collaborative staff development.</p><p>Participants commit
  to 1 hour per week for 4 weeks in beginningSept. 6 and ending Oct. 3.<b>&n
 bsp\;</b></p><p><b>Week of Sept. 6&nbsp\;</b>Buddies are introduced via ema
 il. Identify the top three opportunities you have this month that you’d lik
 e your buddy to observe.&nbsp\;</p><p><b>Sept. 12 at 12pm ET:</b>&nbsp\;Kic
 koff meeting.</p><p><b>Week of Sept. 19:</b>&nbsp\;Shadow your buddy\, or v
 ice versa.</p><p><b>Week of Sept. 26:</b>&nbsp\;Switch! Buddy shadows you\,
  or vice versa. Debrief together and discuss what you both observed and wha
 t may be valuable to share back with the whole group during our debrief cal
 l at the end of the month.</p><p><b>Oct. 3 at 12pm ET:</b>&nbsp\;Debrief me
 eting.&nbsp\;</p><p><a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScbcg
 42M66mAfrY6kXW_-xqFHQxpeV2cwvTmqPM5eetOebLbA/viewform" id="ow1799" __is_own
 er="true"><u>Register here</u></a>.</p></html-blob>
