DESCRIPTION:Journalists don't usually get to tell their own stories. But\, 
 we're changing that – because it has to. We're hosting a National Town Hall
  with journalists who've been targeted for doing their jobs.During this adm
 inistration\, we have seen clear hallmarks of authoritarianism that threate
 n free speech and put the future of the news industry at risk. We have seen
  this pattern play out around the world\, and it demands action.This town h
 all is for readers\, journalists and the general public—a clarion call in a
  time of crisis.<br><br>Register here:<br><a href="https://us06web.zoom.us/
 webinar/register/WN_k7nwO-Y-RomtVUpp2tdcSw#/registration">https://us06web.z
 oom.us/webinar/register/WN_k7nwO-Y-RomtVUpp2tdcSw#/registration</a>
