UID:4bkqc5ua77ns9ja41nv2t9iq0c@google.com
CREATED:20231205T220313Z
DESCRIPTION:Our friends at Labor Notes have announced the next installment 
 of <a href="https://labornotes.org/events/2024/secrets-successful-organizer
 -februarymarch-series">Secrets of a Successful Organizer</a>\, their excell
 ent virtual workshop series\, and the dates are Feb 20\, Feb 27\, and March
  5. So\, we are encouraging NewsGuild members to attend these workshops and
  are rescheduling Strike School workshops!<br><br>The Labor Notes workshop 
 dates are:<br>Feb 20: Beating Apathy<br>Feb 27: Assembling Your Dream Team<
 br>Mar 5: Turning an Issue into a Campaign<br><br>These are excellent works
 hops that will give you the tools you need to build a strong\, striking uni
 on. We encourage you to attend\, AND if you attend all three\, TNG will cov
 er your registration. Sign up for TNG to cover your registration by Feb 16t
 h: <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeMBwszRQaH3rZzDrqbtmN
