 ster/WN_KdHmCSVkQGW-sv_bpx5LUw</a><br><br>After registering\, you will rece
 ive a confirmation email containing information about joining the webinar.<
 br><br><p><span>Meet with community leaders and organized media workers to 
 discuss how we will improve our access to local news\, and how Alden Global
  Capital’s control of Tribune Publishing has already impacted our access to
  local news and reporting. You’ll hear from industry experts\, friends of c
 ommunity news and our readers how we are working together to save our paper
 s from Alden.</span></p><p>&nbsp\;&nbsp\;&nbsp\; <b><span>Notable speakers 
 will include:</span></b></p><p>&nbsp\;&nbsp\;&nbsp\; <span>Rep. Marie Newma
 n\, Illinois 3rd Congressional District representative from Chicago and its
  southwest suburbs</span></p><p>&nbsp\;&nbsp\;&nbsp\; <span>Rep. Jan Schako
 wsky\,&nbsp\; Illinois 9th Congressional District representative</span></p>
