 /u>tZIkceqprDwvHNKw6JLtaL3WOSKL4u<u></u>s96Psc</u></a><br><br>We can build 
 our union by always working to learn and apply new skills and teaching them
  to our co-workers. Join TNG member organizers to hear what folks took away
  from Labor Notes and plan to bring back to all of our fellow members!</blo
 ckquote></blockquote><br><u></u>Join us on the second Saturday of each mont
 h for the national Member Organizer Program monthly meeting! Meet other mem
 ber organizers from around the country\, share challenges and wins\, and pr
 actice organizing skills.<br><br>Each month\, a different member organizer 
 pod will be responsible for developing the agenda\, facilitating the meetin
 g\, and sending out Zoom registration links in advance. Please reach out to
  Hil O'Connell at <a href="mailto:hoconnell@cwa-union.org">hoconnell@cwa-un
 ion.org</a> if you have any questions!<u></u></html-blob>
