 who connect with workers from around the country to share experiences\, dev
 elop skills\, and organize to build power within the labor movement.</p>The
  <b>purpose</b> of the member organizer program is to strengthen our union 
 by developing our members to do the work of our union.<br><br>Come join our
  Biannual meeting to meet members from around the country\, connect\, and b
 rainstorm through organizing topics together.
