DESCRIPTION:This session addresses current events in digital safety for jou
 rnalists\, offering actionable recommendations for: <br><br>1. Evaluating d
 igital security risk in order to prioritize protective measures <br>2. Prot
 ecting accounts\, devices\, and communications with secure passwords and 2F
 A <br>3. Safeguarding encrypted communications by shoring up app settings <
 br>4. Protecting devices from digital (e.g. malware) and physical (e.g. dev
 ice search and seizure) harms <br><br>The NewsGuild-CWA hosts this training
  in collaboration with the Freedom of the Press Foundation. <b><br><br>Regi
 ster here:</b> <a href="https://us06web.zoom.us/webinar/register/WN_ntMk3tR
 vRN2iEUOmw9KzaA" target="_blank">https://us06web.zoom.us/webinar/register/W
 N_ntMk3tRvRN2iEUOmw9KzaA</a>
